## ðŸ”„ Phase A: Context & Cost Analysis

### A1-A2: Load Project Context

Read and summarize:
- **MASTER_PRD.md** â€” Product vision, features, target users
- **stack-profile.json** â€” Tech stack, especially payment provider
- **package.json** â€” Dependencies for cost estimation

### A3: Calculate COGS (Cost of Goods Sold)

**For AI Apps - Critical Cost Factors:**

```markdown
## ðŸ’° COGS Analysis

### Variable Costs Per User (Monthly)

| Cost Center | Calculation | Monthly Cost |
|-------------|-------------|--------------|
| **AI Tokens** | [model] Ã— [avg requests] Ã— [tokens/request] | $X.XX |
| **Database** | [storage GB] Ã— [rate] + [compute] | $X.XX |
| **File Storage** | [avg GB/user] Ã— [rate] | $X.XX |
| **Email/Notifications** | [emails/month] Ã— [rate] | $X.XX |
| **Third-party APIs** | [calls/month] Ã— [rate] | $X.XX |
| **Support Allocation** | [avg tickets] Ã— [cost/ticket] | $X.XX |
| **TOTAL COGS/USER** | | **$X.XX** |

### Pricing Floor Calculation

- COGS/user: $X.XX/month
- Minimum 3x margin: $X.XX/month
- Target 5x margin (SaaS standard): $X.XX/month
- Premium 10x margin (if value supports): $X.XX/month

### Credit/Usage Considerations (if applicable)

| Usage Tier | Credits/Month | AI Calls | Storage | Price Floor |
|------------|---------------|----------|---------|-------------|
| Starter | X | Y | Z GB | $XX |
| Pro | X | Y | Z GB | $XX |
| Enterprise | Unlimited | Y | Z GB | $XX |
```

